        </div>

    </div>

    <div class="banner clearfix">

        <div class="wrapper">

            <div class="image" style="background-image: url('images/banners/marcus-bointon-july-2015.png');"></div>

            <div class="info">
                <h3>Next Event - Modern networking for PHP developers</h3>
                <p>
                    6th July 2015 - <a href="https://twitter.com/SynchroM">Marcus Bointon</a><br/>
                    Talk 6-7pm <a href="https://www.google.co.uk/maps/place/Westbourne+Library/">Westbourne Library</a><br/>
                    Social 7pm+ <a  href="https://www.google.co.uk/maps/place/Camden+Bar+Westbourne">Camden Bar</a>
                </p>

                <a class="btn" href="https://marcusbointon-php-dorset-july-2015.eventbrite.co.uk">
                    <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-qrcode" aria-hidden="true"></span>&nbsp;&nbsp;Free Registration
                </a>

            </div>

        </div>

    </div>

    <div class="banner clearfix" id="southcoast">

        <div class="wrapper">

            <div class="info">
                <h4>PHPDorset Tees and Hoodies</h4>
                <p>Show your support for PHPDorset</p>

                <a class="btn" href="http://phpdorset.spreadshirt.co.uk/" target="_blank">
                    <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-new-window" aria-hidden="true"></span>&nbsp;&nbsp;Visit the store
                </a>
            </div>

            <div class="image" style="background-image: url('images/banners/swag.jpg');"></div>

        </div>

    </div>

    <div id="sponsors">

        <div class="wrapper">

            <h5>Sponsors</h5>

            <div>
                <a href="http://shop.oreilly.com/">
                    <img src="/images/orm.jpg" alt="O'Reilly User Group Program" />
